    "description": "<strong>欢迎来到满月套餐！</strong><br><br>让我们一起放松心情，享受一个宁静的游泳池吧！<br>您将得到一个完整的套件，您可以享受游泳池假期！ 从天而降！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/6a1492963a6ed8d334a96e3866317c64.poster.avif?t=1678101146\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/6a1492963a6ed8d334a96e3866317c64.webm?t=1678101146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/6a1492963a6ed8d334a96e3866317c64.mp4?t=1678101146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><i>满月套装是什么游戏？</i></strong><br><br>用游泳玩具找点点心吧！<br>只要注意或控制游泳的动物就可以了。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/13690639cafdbfadaadc3e5e692f1824.poster.avif?t=1678101146\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/13690639cafdbfadaadc3e5e692f1824.webm?t=1678101146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/13690639cafdbfadaadc3e5e692f1824.mp4?t=1678101146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong><i>这有什么乐趣？</i></strong><br><br>可以一边自由地控制玩具一边放松和游泳。<br>收集超过90+个动物朋友！<br>你可以骑喷泉和跳板。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/9f02781ef913d68e8b8366b2a9cc6a8d.poster.avif?t=1678101146\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/9f02781ef913d68e8b8366b2a9cc6a8d.webm?t=1678101146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/9f02781ef913d68e8b8366b2a9cc6a8d.mp4?t=1678101146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>神秘的极光闪耀着，增添了敏感性。</strong><br><br>在凉爽美丽的游泳池里享受舒适的治愈吧。<br>屏住呼吸，热爱潜水！<br>和可爱的朋友一起享受你的生活吧！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/85aa6267ab3a0a42751c9b9e79a7dde1.poster.avif?t=1678101146\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/85aa6267ab3a0a42751c9b9e79a7dde1.webm?t=1678101146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204220/extras/85aa6267ab3a0a42751c9b9e79a7dde1.mp4?t=1678101146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
